h1. scaffolding

h2. Purpose

The @scaffolding@ plugin configures Grails' support for CRUD via [Scaffolding|guide:scaffolding].

h2. Examples

An example of enabling "dynamic" scaffolding:

{code:java}
class BookController {
    static scaffold = true
}
{code}

h2. Description

Refer to the section on [Scaffolding|guide:scaffolding] in the Grails user guide which details Grails' scaffolding support.
